What is the state of the INSERT after this sequence?

questions.context:
WITH dept_totals AS (
  SELECT department_id, SUM(salary) AS total_sal
    FROM employees
   GROUP BY department_id
)
SELECT * FROM dept_totals WHERE total_sal > 50000;

SELECT employee_id, commission_pct
FROM employees
ORDER BY commission_pct DESC;

questions.text:
Which statement is true about these two queries, both intended to list each employee's last name alongside their manager's last name, including employees who have no manager (such as the company president)?

Query 1: SELECT e.last_name AS employee, m.last_name AS manager FROM employees e LEFT JOIN employees m ON e.manager_id = m.employee_id;

Query 2: SELECT e.last_name AS employee, m.last_name AS manager FROM employees e, employees m WHERE e.manager_id = m.employee_id(+);

